# Warmers

Cache pre-population and predictive caching strategies

## Overview

The `warmers` submodule provides cache pre-population and predictive caching strategies.

## Installation

This submodule is part of the Codomyrmex platform and is installed with the main package.

```bash
pip install codomyrmex
```
